node.title: Death of 5yo boy treated as suspicious
node.description: Police have launched an investigation after a five-year-old Tauranga boy died this morning.
node.content:
["Police have launched an investigation after a five-year-old Tauranga boy died in a hospital this morning.", "", "
The young boy was treated in Tauranga Hospital before being airlifted to Starship Children's Hospital. Photo: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly
", "Detective Senior Sergeant Craig Rawlinson said the death was being treated as suspicious and a post mortem was underway.", "Emergency services were initially called to the Te Puna property in the Bay of Plenty on 1 November after the boy was found with injuries.", "He was treated in Tauranga Hospital before being airlifted to Starship Children's Hospital.", "Rawlinson said a further update would be available following the post mortem."]
